00:19:40.900 --> 00:19:43.550
What is it that would tell us if it was going rogue

00:19:43.550 --> 00:19:43.670
?

00:19:43.700 --> 00:19:45.690
I don't know if that's clear to some people.

00:19:45.690 --> 00:19:46.690
It's not clear to me.

00:19:46.840 --> 00:19:49.680
So – and the later we leave this, the harder it

00:19:49.680 --> 00:19:52.090
is to figure it out, not least because we'll have

00:19:52.140 --> 00:19:53.610
all the factional squabbling.

00:19:53.620 --> 00:19:57.380
So some more things – some practical things you can do.

00:19:57.380 --> 00:20:00.100
Keep your ID self-authenticating, right?

00:20:00.100 --> 00:20:03.090
So remember I said earlier we had the blessed dids where

00:20:03.230 --> 00:20:06.550
you could fully validate just from available data, and we had

00:20:06.550 --> 00:20:09.050
the cursed dids with Sadako crawling out of your TV

