or we had, like, potentially somebody could create a data

00:20:15.010 --> 00:20:17.150
fork in the timeline.

00:20:17.150 --> 00:20:20.180
So if you keep your own rotation key, if, when

00:20:20.180 --> 00:20:21.650
you sign up, you make your own – make your own

00:20:21.650 --> 00:20:23.890
rotation key, write down the seed phrase or whatever you do

00:20:24.040 --> 00:20:27.220
, and don't lose that, you probably never need to

00:20:27.320 --> 00:20:28.200
change it, right?

