It's better if you can just go straight to the PD

00:20:46.400 --> 00:20:48.260
S, and that way you don't have this rotation key

00:20:48.260 --> 00:20:50.580
in your history that is controlled by Blue Sky.

00:20:50.660 --> 00:20:54.490
I don't quite – okay, I put don't use

00:20:54.500 --> 00:20:54.660
it.

